    "description": "If you're a passionate Risk Analyst with drive and ambition, New India Assurance in Kolkata is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout New India Assurance:\nNew India Assurance is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with New India Assurance!",
